css :hover card tip 👨‍🍳

add a small animation + remove transition on :hover

.card { transition: transform 0.2s; }
.card:hover { transition: none;
animation: set backwards 0.2s; }
@​keyframes set {
0% { transform: rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg); }
}

gets rid of snap jumps + lag ⚡ https://t.co/FEDjyd3rlh

